{"tid":2322714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國大選] [突發] 賓州259州長確診武肺","createTime":"2020-12-12T13:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T13:58:15.000Z","uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"83f48b01ac4dfd62c013404cac6c0478efac443d","tid":2322714,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVz4vtG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVz4vtG.png&h=cc0e74bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國賓州民主黨籍的州長沃爾夫（Tom Wolf）因確診武漢肺炎，現正進行居家隔離。<br />\n<br />\n目前為第2任期的沃爾夫透過聲明表示，他是在周二（8日）例行性篩檢時發現確診。他聲稱：「我沒有症狀，感覺良好」、「我遵照美國疾病防治中心（CDC）和衛生部的行動方針（自我隔離）。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCaLeVu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCaLeVu.jpg&h=67c8934b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賓夕法尼亞州州長沃爾夫<br />\n<br />\n最緊要人有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}